--- In Read_Alphabet@yahoogroups.com, Sid Tanaban <sidban2@...> wrote:
>
> I am wondering if there is a list I could copy that would help me to read Read's Alphabet
> Sid
>

A few years ago I made a set of tutorials based on "Alice In Wonderland". You can download from this site at- http://groups.yahoo.com/group/Read_Alphabet/files/Tutorials/Progressive reading tutorials/

Please note: these tutorials are based heavily on the General Australian accent and some words are spelled contrary to the manual.
